Former Marine Jesse Kidder was chasing Michael Wilcox, 27, in New Richmond on Thursday when they stopped and continued the confrontation on foot .
Wilcox, who allegedly gunned down his fiance and best friend, then asked Kidder to shoot him .
Kidder refused and said: 'Shoot me or I'll shoot you'
The officer had been warned by dispatchers before he arrived at the scene .
The Purple Heart winner has been praised for 'restraint and maturity'